{"tid":1039973,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1816號 貝碧嘉（20W）","createTime":"2019-02-27T19:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T19:14:54.000Z","uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ee4ee38d58cf9ca56cc4f8c9c432d7fd0e29b3","tid":1039973,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T19:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 貝碧嘉</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1816號熱帶氣旋 貝碧嘉 BEBINCA(20W) </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：澳門<br />\n意義：貝碧嘉是一種牛奶布丁，澳門人喜愛的食物，可於澳門的葡國餐廳找到。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/31/Bebinca_com_gelado.jpg/1200px-Bebinca_com_gelado.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F3%2F31%2FBebinca_com_gelado.jpg%2F1200px-Bebinca_com_gelado.jpg&h=62a4db08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。 <br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/phDMEEd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FphDMEEd.png&h=c68c509c&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=6c8f78ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/OSjok6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FOSjok6Z.png&h=fc73419e&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=78bd8276\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBZfpfrS.png&h=9df3da65&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d74c82e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a></span></em> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1816.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1816.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_1816.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1816-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1816-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/1816-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://pzal.ndbc.noaa.gov/collab/jtwc/products/wp2018.gif\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201820W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/BEBINCA.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"}]}